{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6169cf67a5","title":"给刘昆林“的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9ee4b020e8","index":0,"year":1945,"month":1,"day":11,"articleId":"6169cf67a5"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji19","name":"毛泽东全集第19卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji19.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji19":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"92af62360a","type":"paragraph","text":"给刘昆林“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"6169cf67a5"},{"id":"f132c281bb","type":"paragraph","text":"1945年1月11日）昆林同志：一谈。来信收到。此信及以前各信均已转给中组部，并请他们找你你长期不被信任，难怪你不满意。但真金不怕火烧，还是应该有耐心，等候同志们了解你，除此都不是出路。看你此次的信，你的问题似平可以获得解决了，更希望你耐心等候。谈吧。这一向题忙，我们哲时不谈。你在延安有一个停留，将来再此致同志的敬礼！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"6169cf67a5"},{"id":"6963757909","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"6169cf67a5"},{"id":"f4211216ae","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十一日[1]刘昆林（1898-1980），湖南桃江人。当时是中共中央党校学员。有晟林用中书书市所","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"6169cf67a5"},{"id":"9defa3d861","type":"paragraph","text":"S月续","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"6169cf67a5"},{"id":"dd6d276d74","type":"paragraph","text":"但真全不文线候到们源你此新成此的的信，你门的孩新1克成推是一尚藏，我经的功方你有续有种而，消丰再该统。共孩同点的承乳！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"6169cf67a5"}],"page":{"id":"4d5e8e92aa","publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"6169cf67a5","start":283,"end":284}}}},"__N_SSG":true}